org.gvsig.fmap.dal.feature

Interface FeatureStoreTransforms

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultFeatureStoreTransforms, FeatureTypeManager.FeatureTypeManagerFeatureStoreTransforms

    public interface FeatureStoreTransforms
extends Cloneable
    This interface represents a container for store transforms. Provides access to transforms by index and by iterator, and also allows adding and removing transforms.
